xposition «Développement inclus» de Leslie Piché et Carolane Saint-Pierre</a></h4><a href="https://www.uneq.qc.ca/evenement/exposition-developpement-inclus/"><img width="300" height="300" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAEACAkQBADs=" data-lazy-src="https://www.uneq.qc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/DeveloppInclusCarre-300x300.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium wp-post-image" alt="DeveloppInclusCarre" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.uneq.qc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/DeveloppInclusCarre-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.uneq.qc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/DeveloppInclusCarre-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.uneq.qc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/DeveloppInclusCarre.jpg 503w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /><noscript><img width="300" height="300" src="https://www.uneq.qc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/DeveloppInclusCarre-300x300.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium wp-post-image" alt="DeveloppInclusCarre" srcset="https://www.uneq.qc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/DeveloppInclusCarre-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.uneq.qc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/DeveloppInclusCarre-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.uneq.qc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/DeveloppInclusCarre.jpg 503w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></noscript></a></li><li class="ecs-event"><span class="duration time"><span class="tribe-event-date-start">10 Mai. @ 18 h 00</span> - <span class="tribe-event-time">20 h 00</span></span><h4 class="entry-title summary"><a href="https://www.uneq.qc.ca/evenement/assemblee-annuelle-centre-teilhard-de-chardin-poesie-claire-silvera-rochon/" rel="bookmark">Assemblée annuelle du Centre Teilhard de Chardin et poésie par Claire Silvera Rochon</a></h4></li><li class="ecs-event"><span class="duration time"><span class="tribe-event-date-start">11 Mai. @ 18 h 00</span> - <span class="tribe-event-time">20 h 00</span></span><h4 class="entry-title summary"><a href="https://www.uneq.qc.ca/evenement/lancement-de-kuei-te-salue/" rel="bookmark">Lancement de « Kuei, je te salue &#8211; conversation sur le racisme » de Deni Ellis Béchard et Natasha Kanapé Fontaine</a></h4><a href="https://www.uneq.qc.ca/evenement/lancement-de-kuei-te-salue/"><img width="300" height="300" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAEACAkQBADs=" data-lazy-src="https://www.uneq.qc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Invitation_Kuei_lancement-2-e1461787267324-300x300.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium wp-post-image" alt="Invitation_Kuei_lancement" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.uneq.qc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Invitation_Kuei_lancement-2-e1461787267324-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.uneq.qc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Invitation_Kuei_lancement-2-e1461787267324-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.uneq.qc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Invitation_Kuei_lancement-2-e1461787267324-768x768.jpg 768w, https://www.uneq.qc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Invitation_Kuei_lancement-2-e1461787267324-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://www.uneq.qc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Invitation_Kuei_lancement-2-e1461787267324.jpg 1356w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /><noscript><img width="300" height="300" src="https://www.uneq.qc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Invitation_Kuei_lancement-2-e1461787267324-300x300.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium wp-post-image" alt="Invitation_Kuei_lancement" srcset="https://www.uneq.qc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Invitation_Kuei_lancement-2-e1461787267324-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.uneq.qc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Invitation_Kuei_lancement-2-e1461787267324-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.uneq.qc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Invitation_Kuei_lancement-2-e1461787267324-768x768.jpg 768w, https://www.uneq.qc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Invitation_Kuei_lancement-2-e1461787267324-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://www.uneq.qc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Invitation_Kuei_lancement-2-e1461787267324.jpg 1356w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></noscript></a></li></ul></div><div cla